<cb:div>
<lb ed="I" n="0231b01" type="honorific"/><p xml:id="pI01p0231b0101">大齊天統五年歲
<lb ed="I" n="0231b02" type="honorific"/>次己丑四月<note n="0231001" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB31071"/>＝庚【史】</note><note n="0231001" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB31071"/>【佛拓】，庚【史】</note><app n="0231001"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">庚</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB31071"/></rdg></app>申
<lb ed="I" n="0231b03" type="honorific"/>朔八日丁卯建</p>
</cb:div>
<cb:div>
<lb ed="I" n="0231c01" type="honorific"/><p xml:id="pI01p0231c0101">蓋若道非真極玄元。言<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">情</unclear>万
<lb ed="I" n="0231c02" type="honorific"/>類之表。誰有辭城棄位。以布
<lb ed="I" n="0231c03" type="honorific"/>衣為好者也。若夫芳蓉<note n="0231002" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB31072"/>＝姿【史】</note><note n="0231002" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB31072"/>【佛拓】，姿【史】</note><app n="0231002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">姿</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB31072"/></rdg></app>婉。
<lb ed="I" n="0231c04" type="honorific"/>重爵名官。思皆浮庶。仕民□
<lb ed="I" n="0231c05" type="honorific"/>情貪暮。自不貨身<note n="0231003" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">筫＝質【史】</note><note n="0231003" resp="ihp" type="mod">筫【佛拓】，質【史】</note><app n="0231003"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">質</lem><rdg wit="【原】">筫</rdg></app><note n="0231004" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB18861"/>＝肉【史】</note><note n="0231004" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB18861"/>【佛拓】，肉【史】</note><app n="0231004"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">肉</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB18861"/></rdg></app>。布<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">髮</unclear>
<lb ed="I" n="0231c06" type="honorific"/>淹泥之徒。焉有昏閨闇室。更
<lb ed="I" n="0231c07" type="honorific"/>續明燈者怖。今都唯那潘景
<lb ed="I" n="0231c08" type="honorific"/>暉。張煞鬼。李仕暉。陽脩羅。仰
<lb ed="I" n="0231c09" type="honorific"/>率儒徒七十人等。並雍容雅
<lb ed="I" n="0231c10" type="honorific"/>素。若孤鵠沖天。綺結<note n="0231005" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB31073"/>＝蔥【史】</note><note n="0231005" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB31073"/>【佛拓】，蔥【史】</note><app n="0231005"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">蔥</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB31073"/></rdg></app>紅。似
<lb ed="I" n="0231c11" type="honorific"/>群龍集主渚。往曾竹馬餘暇。
<lb ed="I" n="0231c12" type="honorific"/>縕五禮以俱融。長復脩多。知
<lb ed="I" n="0231c13" type="honorific"/>四藏而弘解。常願乘風出谷。
<lb ed="I" n="0231c14" type="honorific"/><note n="0231006" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB21570"/>＝衿【史】</note><note n="0231006" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB21570"/>【佛拓】，衿【史】</note><app n="0231006"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">衿</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB21570"/></rdg></app>濟群生。龍宮陃教。昕階大
<lb ed="I" n="0231c15" type="honorific"/>道。但惕聖之已去。逍迢金山。
<lb ed="I" n="0231c16" type="honorific"/>薨巔既<note n="0231007" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">又＝久【史】</note><note n="0231007" resp="ihp" type="mod">又【佛拓】，久【史】</note><app n="0231007"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">久</lem><rdg wit="【原】">又</rdg></app>。若不矸彫神狀。想
<lb ed="I" n="0231c17" type="honorific"/><note n="0231008" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB25577"/>＝作【史】</note><note n="0231008" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB25577"/>【佛拓】，作【史】</note><app n="0231008"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">作</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB25577"/></rdg></app>當時。<note n="0231009" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB31173"/>＝無【史】</note><note n="0231009" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB31173"/>【佛拓】，無【史】</note><app n="0231009"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">無</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB31173"/></rdg></app>以紹述嚴議。弘輪
<lb ed="I" n="0231c18" type="honorific"/>更轉。是以<note n="0231010" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30558"/>＝遠【史】</note><note n="0231010" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30558"/>【佛拓】，遠【史】</note><app n="0231010"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">遠</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30558"/></rdg></app>詣浮山嶺岫。取
<lb ed="I" n="0231c19" type="honorific"/>玉類之純貞。還對泉源。礱磨
<lb ed="I" n="0231c20" type="honorific"/>彫<note n="0231011" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">硺＝琢【史】</note><note n="0231011" resp="ihp" type="mod">硺【佛拓】，琢【史】</note><app n="0231011"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">琢</lem><rdg wit="【原】">硺</rdg></app>。造碑像一<note n="0231012" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB31074"/>＝區【史】</note><note n="0231012" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB31074"/>【佛拓】，區【史】</note><app n="0231012"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">區</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB31074"/></rdg></app>。二侗菩薩。
<lb ed="I" n="0231c21" type="honorific"/>北面開光。方侵上頂。因茲妙
<lb ed="I" n="0231c22" type="honorific"/>瑞。仰諮皇帝。化九夷而同風。
<lb ed="I" n="0231c23" type="honorific"/><note n="0231013" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">棇＝總【史】</note><note n="0231013" resp="ihp" type="mod">棇【佛拓】，總【史】</note><app n="0231013"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">總</lem><rdg wit="【原】">棇</rdg></app>万國以隆強。四王奉<note n="0231014" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB31075"/>＝華【史】</note><note n="0231014" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB31075"/>【佛拓】，華【史】</note><app n="0231014"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">華</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB31075"/></rdg></app>於
<lb ed="I" n="0231c24" type="honorific"/>玉珮。諸天貢寶於金葙。<note n="0231015" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">逯＝逮【史】</note><note n="0231015" resp="ihp" type="mod">逯【佛拓】，逮【史】</note><app n="0231015"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">逮</lem><rdg wit="【原】">逯</rdg></app>及
<lb ed="I" n="0231c25" type="honorific"/>七祖先零。圓通六道。俱證金<note n="0231016" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB31076"/>＝剛【史】</note><note n="0231016" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB31076"/>【佛拓】，剛【史】</note><app n="0231016"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">剛</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB31076"/></rdg></app>。
<lb ed="I" n="0231c26" type="honorific"/>其辭曰　沖<note n="0231017" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB08512"/>＝寂【史】</note><note n="0231017" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB08512"/>【佛拓】，寂【史】</note><app n="0231017"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">寂</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB08512"/></rdg></app>妙絕。超越是非。凡
<lb ed="I" n="0231c27" type="honorific"/>情未達。聖者<note n="0231018" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB31077"/>＝能【史】</note><note n="0231018" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB31077"/>【佛拓】，能【史】</note><app n="0231018"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">能</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB31077"/></rdg></app>歸。巧存方便。<note n="0231019" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB04294"/>＝貿【史】</note><note n="0231019" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB04294"/>【佛拓】，貿【史】</note><app n="0231019"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">貿</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB04294"/></rdg></app><unclear cert="low" reason="damage">易</unclear>
<lb ed="I" n="0231c28" type="honorific"/><note n="0231020" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB31078"/>＝粗【史】</note><note n="0231020" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB31078"/>【佛拓】，粗【史】</note><app n="0231020"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">粗</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB31078"/></rdg></app>衣。<note place="inline">一</note>榮名麗仕。美<note n="0231021" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">艶＝豔【史】</note><note n="0231021" resp="ihp" type="mod">艶【佛拓】，豔【史】</note><app n="0231021"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">豔</lem><rdg wit="【原】">艶</rdg></app>垂紅。斯皆危
<lb ed="I" n="0231c29" type="honorific"/>毳。未若真蹤。波論自<note n="0231022" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB31079"/>＝鬻【史】</note><note n="0231022" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB31079"/>【佛拓】，鬻【史】</note><app n="0231022"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">鬻</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB31079"/></rdg></app>。<note n="0231023" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB31080"/>＝嚮【史】</note><note n="0231023" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB31080"/>【佛拓】，嚮【史】</note><app n="0231023"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">嚮</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB31080"/></rdg></app>勸鱗空。<note place="inline">二</note>
<lb ed="I" n="0231c30" type="honorific"/>昏〃六道。<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">快</unclear>似深閨。<note n="0231c3001" resp="CBETA" type="add">无【CB】，旡【原】【史】</note><app n="0231c3001"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.maha">无</lem><rdg wit="【原】 【史】">旡</rdg></app>人執炬。終墜<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">泥</unclear>
<lb ed="I" n="0231c31" type="honorific"/><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">梨</unclear>。<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">賴</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">茲</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">明</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">哲</unclear>。<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">濟</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">我</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">群</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">迷</unclear>。<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">昔</unclear>兮<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">五</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">色</unclear>。<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">收</unclear>
<lb ed="I" n="0231c32" type="honorific"/><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">在</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">雙</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">林</unclear>。<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">于</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">時</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">還</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">照</unclear>。<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">視</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">我</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">山</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">金</unclear>。<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">脩</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">功</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">練</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">石</unclear>。<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">長</unclear>
<lb ed="I" n="0231c33" type="honorific"/><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">去</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">幽</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">沈</unclear>。</p>
